"Combine multiple categories into a related set that can be assigned to data "
"elements for dissagregation. Can also be used to to assign metadata "
"attributes to data sets or programs."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Specify code and attributes to enable easier data exchange with other "
"systems."
msgstr ""

